description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

 

The duo are back answering your questions! They’re talking about how they knew they wanted to act, offering advice on being in love with your friend, and the generational divide.

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod
